<body>
Reports an <code>if</code> statement that
can be simplified to a single assignment or
a <code>return</code> statement.  <p>Example:</p>
<pre><code>
if(foo())
 {
  return true;
 }
 else
 {
   return false;
 }
</code></pre>
<p>After applying the quick-fix the code looks as follows:</p>
<pre>
 <code>return foo();</code>
</pre>
</body>
